from the cart.

34:49.989 --> 34:52.389
Tourniquet her arm,
and give me a hemostat.

34:54.360 --> 34:56.260
It's tied.
I-i'm not crazy, sarah.

34:56.295 --> 34:57.695
I-I'm not.

35:17.183 --> 35:19.350
Surgery turned out well today.

35:19.385 --> 35:21.385
Thanks to you, dr. Rhodes.

35:23.389 --> 35:24.667
It's been a long day,
dr. Latham.

