Trafficking of cocaine
is a felony.

35:59.525 --> 36:03.360
That means calling
the dea, homeland,

36:03.396 --> 36:04.829
The whole nine yards.

36:04.864 --> 36:07.531
All that over one packet?

36:07.567 --> 36:11.068
Well, if the evidence
is just this one,

36:11.104 --> 36:15.106
That doesn't demonstrate intent
to traffic and sell.

36:16.542 --> 36:18.109
Were there more?

36:19.679 --> 36:21.712
No.

36:21.748 --> 36:23.614
The one packet is all we found.

36:25.618 --> 36:27.318
That's correct.

36:29.522 --> 36:32.389
Dr. Choi?

36:32.425 --> 36:34.492
Anything to add?

36:36.262 --> 36:38.162
Dr. Choi...

36:42.602 --> 36:44.135
No.

36:47.874 --> 36:50.141
Then that's that.

37:02.789 --> 37:04.555
Thank you, dr. Choi.

37:05.892 --> 37:09.426
Do not put me
in that position again...

37:09.462 --> 37:11.162
Either of you.

37:16.135 --> 37:18.269
I don't know that
I helped zulmera.

37:18.304 --> 37:21.272
She still has to deal with
the people whose drugs she lost.

37:21.307 --> 37:23.440
She is a resourceful woman.

37:23.476 --> 37:24.208
She's gonna do what she needs.

37:24.243 --> 37:25.709
To take care of
that little girl.

37:25.745 --> 37:28.779
I had to at least
try to help her.

37:28.815 --> 37:31.882
If I had a child,
I would've done the same thing.

37:31.918 --> 37:34.185
I know.

37:35.254 --> 37:37.721
Thank you.

37:37.757 --> 37:40.591
And thank you for earlier...

37:40.626 --> 37:42.426
About the baby.

37:49.802 --> 37:52.436
It's my fault.

37:52.471 --> 37:54.238
Why'd you say that?

37:54.273 --> 37:56.473
I gave her false hope.

37:56.509 --> 37:58.175
I told her I believed
she was stable.

37:58.211 --> 38:01.645
When she clearly isn't.
I'm not sure I agree.

38:01.681 --> 38:04.915
I mean, just made her case
a little tougher,

38:04.951 --> 38:08.319
But I'm still gonna
file the appeal.

38:08.354 --> 38:09.486
