39:40.813 --> 39:43.447
I cannot afford that.

39:43.482 --> 39:46.650
I'm ending my treatments,
at least for the time being.

39:48.087 --> 39:49.264
Well, I'm sorry that
you feel like.

39:49.288 --> 39:52.890
You have to make that decision,
but I trust your judgement.

39:56.595 --> 39:57.928
When you started
your fellowship,

39:57.964 --> 40:00.831
I told you that
you were not my first choice.

40:02.969 --> 40:04.868
After working with you
these last months,

40:04.904 --> 40:07.404
I would like to say that
I cannot imagine.

40:07.440 --> 40:11.342
A finer surgeon or person
than you, dr. Rhodes.

40:14.480 --> 40:16.046
Thank you.

40:17.850 --> 40:21.051
Well, let's leave it at that.
Yeah.

40:21.087 --> 40:25.789
I would like a drink.
Scotch for me... neat.

40:25.825 --> 40:29.360
